# Treat the Xcode project as text and union-merge it: when two branches each add
# an object, keep both sides' lines instead of conflicting. With Xcode's
# filesystem-synchronized groups, file add/remove no longer touches this file at
# all, so conflicts are rare — this is cheap insurance. (Vanilla-Xcode decision;
# see QUALITY.md "Project gen".)
*.pbxproj merge=union
*.pbxproj -diff
